  <brief_title>A 6 Months NIS to Evaluate the Use of Rescue Medication and Quality of Life in Adult Asthmatic Subjects Treated With Symbicort® SMART®</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 6 Months NIS to Evaluate the Use of Rescue Medication and Quality of Life in Adult Asthmatic Subjects Treated With Symbicort® SMART® 1-2 Inhalations b.i.d. as Maintenance Therapy Plus Additional Inhalations As-needed, Compared to Patients Treated With a Free Combination of an Inhaled Glucocorticosteroid and an Inhaled Long Acting ß2-agonist Plus as Needed Inhalations of a Short Acting ß2 Agonist.</official_title>
