  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to describe the use of rescue medication and quality of life in
      adult asthmatic patients, either treated with SYMBICORT SMART® (regular dose according to
      physician's prescription and the current summary of product characteristics - SPC) or treated
      with a free combination of ICS plus LABA plus as needed SABA prescribed by the physician.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
